THE Usage the Actors have re∣ceived from him, urged me,
The meanest in Renown;
The poorest Trifler of the Town, to twirl a Sling against this Classical Goliah; for, I think, every Person belonging to the Theatres, has a Right to treat that Man with Ridicule, who endeavours to throw them into Con∣tempt.
